[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[[Memory]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]

Swaps:

swapon -s

or

cat /proc/swaps

[See swap info in system]

---------------------------------------------------------------

lsblk -o TYPE,NAME,KNAME,UUID,MOUNTPOINT,SIZE

[To see all partitions (including swap memory partition)]

---------------------------------------------------------------

free -h

[To see used and free swap memory]

---------------------------------------------------------------

swapoff -a && swapon -a

[To free swap memory]

---------------------------------------------------------------







